<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>One of the most interesting and genuinely fun projects of my career. Bao has been obsessed with Chinese Pokemon cards for years, and he opened his shop and online platforms just a few months before they completely exploded on the western market. Today he does not have time to answer the phone.</p>
    <p>I still handle the visual identity of the physical store, some events, and we are working on a proper online portal to replace the current placeholder site. Working with someone who has that level of real passion for what they do is rare and it shows in everything.</p>
